00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:07.800
Are you saying that the answer you’ve been looking for about your dream...

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:12.560
has something to do with our past lives?

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:16.760
That you are the Garuda and I’m the Naga...

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:22.320
I’m that woman who often appears in your dream?

00:02:25.079 --> 00:02:25.840
Yeah.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:34.680
Wansarut, you and I have been in love since our past lives.

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.000
But the war between our kinds...

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:44.800
brought us to death as if we had been cursed.

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:50.920
The shadow that has been trying to attack me all this time...

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.920
is another Naga.

00:02:58.040 --> 00:03:01.080
He tries to separate you from me so that we can’t be together.

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:04.800
So...

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:09.960
that Naga shadow also exists in this life.

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:13.080
Who is he?

00:03:23.160 --> 00:03:26.680
Why do you want me to keep it a secret from Tharn? Why can’t I tell him about Chalothorn?

00:03:27.160 --> 00:03:31.360
If Tharn knows, he will surely do something.

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:34.320
He will try to stop Chalothorn.

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:37.040
And might try to settle things by himself.

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:43.560
The 15th night of the 11th moon is coming soon.

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:45.720
You must be careful and don’t let Chalothorn get close to Tharn.

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:50.600
Protect him from whatever that might make him in danger.

00:03:51.560 --> 00:03:53.600
Once the 15th night of the 11th waxing moon has passed,

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:58.360
Tharn will then be free from the karma and those whom he has done wrong in the past. Am I right?

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.440
If possible,

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.040
- I want Tharn to come stay with me...
- Okay

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:06.640
until the Day of Judgement has passed.

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:28.480
So, every time when an unexplainable incident occured…

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:33.080
in every case that both of us were working on,

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:38.520
whether those incidents at the training camp...

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:48.680
or the ones during Narong and Art’s cases. Did all those happen because of that man?

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:58.280
Listen to me, Tharn.

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:01.040
No matter what is going happen.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:10.320
I’ll always be by your side to protect you.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:19.080
The prophecy that the Abbot used to tell us when we were young…

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:22.560
is about to happen inevitably.

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:27.960
You’ll be in danger because of me.

00:05:28.520 --> 00:05:30.120
Just like my parents.

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:35.360
Hey, he can’t harm me.

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.240
I have this amulet with me.

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:51.040
Don’t you worry. I’m not going to leave you again.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:59.159
If we can’t avoid what’s going to happen,

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:04.280
maybe running away is not the right answer anymore.

00:06:05.760 --> 00:06:06.480
Yeah.

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:17.600
Since I still have to recover...

00:06:17.880 --> 00:06:19.600
and you’re suspeneded from work,

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:24.960
should we go see the Abbot?

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:28.840
I can’t right now.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:33.520
I need to find out the truth.

00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:36.920
I need to know if Chart is related to the killer who murdered my parents.

00:06:40.920 --> 00:06:43.400
Khem is taking care of it right now.

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:53.800
I want you to use this time during your suspension...

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:56.360
to take some rest for a while.

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:04.840
I’ll help you find out about your parent’s case.

00:07:06.440 --> 00:07:11.680
Let’s go see the Abbot in Nongkai together, okay?

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.280
Please?

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:21.360
Okay.

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:37.520
Oh, there’s one more thing.

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:40.680
Yes?

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:48.200
If Chalothorn comes to see you or ask you to go anywhere with him,

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:50.680
you must tell me right the way.

00:07:52.400 --> 00:07:56.440
Don’t go anywhere with him alone, okay?

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:58.800
Why?

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:05.640
I’m jealous. Is that reasonable enough?

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:13.560
Don’t go anywhere with him again, okay? I’m begging you.

00:08:14.640 --> 00:08:15.840
Please, Tharn.

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:19.400
Fine, you don’t have to worry about that though.

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:24.680
I’m sure he’s quite fed up to quarrel with you.

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:31.360
He didn’t even call or text me during the past few days.

00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:39.280
Did he tell you where he’d go?

00:08:43.720 --> 00:08:45.040
He didn’t tell me anything.

00:08:46.120 --> 00:08:47.280
I don’t know what he’s doing either.

00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:51.040
Is that so?

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:52.120
Yeah.

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:03.760
Huh? Why is it not charging?

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:09.560
Geez, he forgot to plug it in.

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.680
Now we don’t know if Yai has called about the case.

